{"article_id":"2qQczPHqEWiZHWnG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Attorney General Jeff Sessions","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Jefferson","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"( Jeff ) Beauregard SessionsMedill dean","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"'deeply troubled by the vicious bullying and badgering ' of student journalists","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"Trump has considered firing official","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"who reported whistleblower complaint to Congress :","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"report","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Northwestern student paper apologizes for coverage of 'traumatic ' Jeff Sessions event","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"MORE said early Thursday","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that he would be willing to recuse himself from any investigation of Russian involvement in President Trump 's campaign","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"if it 's `` appropriate . ''","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"`` I have said","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"whenever it 's appropriate ,","depth":11},{"id":13,"text":"I will recuse myself , ''","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"he told NBC News .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"`` There 's no doubt about that . ''","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"In @ NBCNews exclusive video AG Sessions says","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"he will recuse himself from Russia investigation","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"whenever appropriate :","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"pic.twitter.com/wKajg9MUJj - Morning Joe","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"( @ Morning_Joe )","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"March 2 , 2017","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Reports emerged late Wednesday","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"that Sessions spoke twice with Russian Ambassador Sergey Kislyak during the 2016 presidential race .","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Sessions did not disclose those conversations during his confirmation hearings for attorney general ,","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"testifying under oath","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"that he \" did not have communications with the Russians . \"","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"Sessions defended himself during his comments with NBC News ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"saying","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"he did n't discuss the presidential campaign with Russian officials .","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"\" Well , I have not met with any Russians at any time","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"to discuss any political campaigns , \"","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` Those remarks are unbelievable to me","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"and are false .","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"I don ' t have anything else","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"to say about that . \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Sessions 's latest comments come","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"as more GOP lawmakers say","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"he might have to recuse himself from any investigation","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"involving Russia and the Trump campaign at the Justice Department .","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"On Thursday morning , House Majority Leader Kevin McCarthy","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"( R-Calif. )","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"suggested","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"it would be `` easier ''","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"if Sessions recused himself from any Russia-related investigations","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"that might come up .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"`` I do n't have all the information in front of me ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"I do n't want to pre-judge ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"but I just think","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"for any investigation","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"going forward ,","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"you want to make sure","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"everybody trusts the investigation , ''","depth":15},{"id":54,"text":"McCarthy said on MSNBC 's `` Morning Joe . ''","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"`` That there 's no doubt within the investigation . ... I think","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"it would be easier from that standpoint , yes . ''","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"The FBI is said to be investigating contact between Russian officials and members of the Trump campaign ,","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"though there has yet to be any formal charges brought .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Committees in the House and Senate are pursuing their own investigations .","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"Sen. Lindsey Graham","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Lindsey Olin GrahamGraham says","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"Trump should be allowed to undo DACA order 's 12:30","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"Report :","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"Dems , GOP dig in for public impeachment hearings 's Morning Report -","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Witness transcripts plow ground for public impeachment testimony","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"MORE","depth":11},{"id":67,"text":"( R-S.C. )","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"on Wednesday said","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"if the FBI finds any criminal activity","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"related to campaign aides ' alleged contact with Russian officials ,","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"then a special prosecutor will likely be needed .","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"Rep. Sean Duffy","depth":9},{"id":74,"text":"Sean DuffyOn The Money :","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Trump seeks to shift spotlight from impeachment to economy |","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Appropriators agree to Dec. 20 funding deadline |","depth":13},{"id":77,"text":"New study says","depth":14},{"id":78,"text":"tariffs threaten 1.5M jobs","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"Ex-Rep. Duffy to join lobbying firm BGR","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Trump 's defenders are running out of options","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"MORE","depth":14},{"id":82,"text":"( R-Wis. ) ,","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"meantime , said","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"he wished","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"Sessions had been `` more clear '' during the confirmation process about his meetings .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"`` It gives me some pause that he was n't more clear about the meeting , ''","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"Duffy said Thursday morning on CNN 's `` New Day . ''","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"`` I think","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"as he 's going through the campaign with Mr. Trump though ,","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"he was acting in his official capacity as a senator ,","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"you want to disclose that information","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"and I think","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"it should have been more clear during his confirmation process","depth":15},{"id":94,"text":"that he did have the meetings . ''","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"Sessions , a former Republican senator from Alabama , reportedly spoke with Kislyak during a July Heritage Foundation event at the Republican National Convention","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"attended by about 50 ambassadors .","depth":12},{"id":97,"text":"A Department of Justice official told The Washington Post","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Kislyak was among a group of diplomats","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"who approached Sessions","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"and spoke with him informally there .","depth":14},{"id":101,"text":"Sessions also spoke with Kislyak via phone in September ,","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"according to a spokeswoman for the attorney general .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"The conversation took place during a time","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"when U.S. intelligence officials assert","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"that Russia was interfering in the 2016 race through a hacking and influence campaign .","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"Reports emerged last month","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"that top aides and allies of Trump ' s White House run were in recurring contact with senior Russian intelligence officials .","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"Democrats seized on news","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"about Sessions speaking with Kislyak ,","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"arguing","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Sessions must recuse himself from any federal in